Sceneplate with HTML menu
=========================

You can interact with the scene from within an HTML page by calling Python functions of the VRED Python API,
as well as custom Python functions defined in the script that comes with the vpb file (Edit > Script Editor).

Use JavaScript to execute Python code in VRED:

.. code-block:: javascript
  :caption: JavaScript
  
  // just calls some Python code
  vred.executePython("setWireframe(SWITCH_TOGGLE)");
  
  // example how to call a Python command with a return value
  vred.executePythonCommand("getFov()", function(value)
    { alert(value); } // do something with the value returned by getFov()
  );

`vred` is a special object that is available in JavaScript when running the web page 
within a VRED web engine. The Python code passed to `executePython` and `executePythonCommand` 
is executed by VRED's Python interpreter, similar to running it in the Terminal or Script Editor.

Example
#######

The example file menu-sceneplate.vpb shows an HTML menu on a Frontplate (Sceneplate Editor).
A click on the buttons triggers an action in the VRED scene, like switching the material and playing an animation.


The Python code in the vpb (Edit > Script Editor) defines functions that are called when clicking on the Top, Left, Bottom, Right buttons in the menu:

.. code-block:: python
  :linenos:
  :caption: menu-sceneplate.vpb

  def dock(dockState):
      node = vrSceneplateService.findNode("Frontplate")
      plate = (vrdSceneplateNode)(node)
      plate.setPosition(dockState) 
      
  def dockLeft():
      dock(vrSceneplateTypes.Left)
      
  def dockRight():
      dock(vrSceneplateTypes.Right)
      
  def dockTop():
      dock(vrSceneplateTypes.Top)
      
  def dockBottom():
      dock(vrSceneplateTypes.Bottom)
        


Html code in sceneplate:

.. code-block:: html
  :linenos:
  :caption: menu-sceneplate.vpb

  <!DOCTYPE html>
  <html>
  <head>
      <meta content="text/html" charset="UTF-8">
      <title>Frontplate whith webcontent</title>

      <style>
          html, body {
              font-family: Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif;
              margin: 0px;
              font-size: 12px;
              color: Orange;
              -webkit-user-select: none;
              overflow: hidden;
          }

          .header {
              margin: 2px;
          }

          .toolbar {
              margin-top: 2px;
          }

          .box, .cone, .cylinder, .circle, .top, .bottom, .left, .right {
              width: 30px;
              height: 30px;
          }
          
          .box {
              background-image: url(data:image/svg+xml;base64,);
          }

          .cylinder {
              background-image: url(data:image/svg+xml;base64,);
          }

          .cone {
              background-image: url(data:image/svg+xml;base64,);
          }

          .circle {
              background-image: url(data:image/svg+xml;base64,);
          }

          .bottom {
              background-image: url(data:image/svg+xml;base64,);
          }

          .left {
              background-image: url(data:image/svg+xml;base64,);
          }

          .right {
              background-image: url(data:image/svg+xml;base64,);
          }

          .top {
              background-image: url(data:image/svg+xml;base64,);
          }

          .png {
              width: 32px;
              height: 32px;
          }

          .rule {
              color: Orange;
              background: Orange;
          }

          .PlateButton {
              background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ededed 5%, #bab1ba 100%);
              background-color: #ededed;
              border-radius: 15px;
              border: 1px solid #d6bcd6;
              display: inline-block;
              width: 50px;
              height: 50px;
              text-align: center;
              color: #3a8a9e;
              font-family: Arial;
              font-size: 17px;
              padding: 7px 17px;
              text-decoration: none;
              text-shadow: 0px 1px 0px #e1e2ed;
          }

              .PlateButton:hover {
                  background-color: #bab1ba;
              }

              .PlateButton:active {
                  position: relative;
                  top: 1px;
              }

          .PlateMenu {
              width: 370px;
              padding: 7px;
              border: 1px solid Orange;
              border-radius: 11px;
              background: linear-gradient(DimGrey 10%,Black 90%);
          }
      </style>

      <script type="text/javascript">        
          var _materials = [
              "value=setSwitchMaterialChoice('SwitchMaterial', 0)",
              "value=setSwitchMaterialChoice('SwitchMaterial', 1)",
              "value=setSwitchMaterialChoice('SwitchMaterial', 2)",
              "value=setSwitchMaterialChoice('SwitchMaterial', 3)"
          ];

          var _shapes = [
              "playCAnimation('Box_Block')",
              "playCAnimation('Cylinder_Block')",
              "playCAnimation('Cone_Block')",
              "playCAnimation('Sphere_Block')"
          ];

          var _dockings = [
              "dockLeft()",
              "dockRight()",
              "dockTop()",
              "dockBottom()"
          ];

          function setColor(color) {
              vred.executePython(_materials[color]);
          }

          function setShape(shape) {
              vred.executePython(_shapes[shape]);
          }

          function setDocking(dock) {
              vred.executePython(_dockings[dock]);
          }
      </script>
  </head>
  <body>
      <div class="PlateMenu">
              <div class="toolbar">
                  <div class="header">Animate</div>
                  <div class="PlateButton" onclick="setShape(0);">
                      <svg class="box png"/>Box
                  </div>
                  <div class="PlateButton" onclick="setShape(1);">
                      <svg class="cylinder png"/>Cylinder
                  </div>
                  <div class="PlateButton" onclick="setShape(2);">
                      <svg class="cone png"/>Cone
                  </div>
                  <div class="PlateButton" onclick="setShape(3);">
                      <svg class="circle png"/>Circle
                  </div>
              </div>

              <div class="toolbar">
                  <div class="header">Color</div>
                  <div class="PlateButton" onclick="setColor(0);">
                      <img class="png" src="data:image/png;base64, " />Pink
                  </div>
                  <div class="PlateButton" onclick="setColor(1);">
                      <img class="png" src="data:image/png;base64, " />Blue
                  </div>
                  <div class="PlateButton" onclick="setColor(2);">
                      <img class="png" src="data:image/png;base64, " />Green
                  </div>

                  <div class="PlateButton" onclick="setColor(3);">
                      <img class="png" src="data:image/png;base64," />Yellow
                  </div>
              </div>

              <div class="toolbar">
                  <div class="header">Dock</div>
                  <div class="PlateButton" onclick="setDocking(0);">
                      <svg class="left" />Left
                  </div>
                  <div class="PlateButton" onclick="setDocking(1);">
                      <svg class="right" />Right
                  </div>
                  <div class="PlateButton" onclick="setDocking(2);">
                      <svg class="top" />
                      Top
                  </div>
                  <div class="PlateButton" onclick="setDocking(3);">
                      <svg class="bottom" />Bottom
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
  </body>
  </html>
